01:04:57,480 --> 01:04:58,850
Nam-il, come with us to the right.

814
01:04:58,930 --> 01:05:00,390
-The rest to the left.
-Okay.

815
01:05:00,480 --> 01:05:01,480
We'll go left.

816
01:05:03,190 --> 01:05:04,440
Be careful everyone.

817
01:05:08,860 --> 01:05:12,570
I wish they told us
exactly where the baby is.

818
01:05:13,160 --> 01:05:16,040
How is "near the patrol division" helpful?
That's a huge area to cover.

819
01:05:17,330 --> 01:05:19,040
We're just about to get off the clock.

820
01:05:19,870 --> 01:05:22,000
Team Two went out right away
to work on another case.

821
01:05:22,080 --> 01:05:24,880
The weather is too cold for a baby too.

822
01:05:25,590 --> 01:05:27,050
I hope they find it soon.

823
01:05:27,840 --> 01:05:28,960
I know.

824
01:05:38,390 --> 01:05:39,480
Wait!

825
01:05:40,020 --> 01:05:42,020
I want to ask you something.

826
01:05:43,230 --> 01:05:44,440
Wait.

827
01:05:44,900 --> 01:05:46,980
Sam-bo, what is it?

828
01:05:47,070 --> 01:05:48,440
I think she's the mom.

829
01:05:48,570 --> 01:05:50,530
She ran off after we made eye contact.

830
01:05:52,360 --> 01:05:54,110
Be careful! There's a car coming.

831
01:06:04,290 --> 01:06:06,250
You go right, I'll go left.

832
01:06:06,340 --> 01:06:07,960
We need to find the mom to find the baby.

833
01:06:08,050 --> 01:06:09,170
-Right.
-Stay safe.

834
01:06:09,260 --> 01:06:10,300
Okay.

835
01:06:10,590 --> 01:06:12,380
She's in her 20s and wears a gray hoodie.

836
01:06:12,470 --> 01:06:14,590
-Okay. Take care.
-You too.

837
01:06:42,660 --> 01:06:44,750
-Did you find the baby, Sang-su?
-No, not yet.

838
01:06:47,290 --> 01:06:48,250
We'll look again.

839
01:07:13,280 --> 01:07:14,450
Oh, no.

840
01:07:37,260 --> 01:07:38,260
I found it!

841
01:07:41,140 --> 01:07:42,970
I think the baby's turning blue!

842
01:07:49,060 --> 01:07:50,520
Its breathing is irregular.

843
01:07:50,940 --> 01:07:53,360
The baby's breathing funny. Help!

844
01:07:54,150 --> 01:07:56,530
Help me, Sergeant Kang!

845
01:07:56,610 --> 01:07:58,990
-Make way.
-Hongil Patrol Division.

846
01:07:59,070 --> 01:08:01,080
-Coming through.
-The baby's freezing.

847
01:08:01,160 --> 01:08:02,620
Turn on the boiler in the restroom!

848
01:08:02,700 --> 01:08:04,370
Seung-jae, get the heating fan.

849
01:08:04,870 --> 01:08:06,250
Get everything in storage.

850
01:08:06,330 --> 01:08:08,170
I can perform CPR on infants.

851
01:08:08,620 --> 01:08:10,170
-Coming through.
-Yes.

852
01:08:10,250 --> 01:08:12,040
-Coming through.
-I took a course.

853
01:08:12,290 --> 01:08:13,550
Come quick!

854
01:08:18,510 --> 01:08:19,590
Shit, where is it?

855
01:08:19,680 --> 01:08:21,350
Where's the heating fan?

856
01:08:23,350 --> 01:08:24,310
Damn it!

857
01:08:25,180 --> 01:08:26,480
I know I saw it somewhere here.

858
01:08:26,770 --> 01:08:29,480
Get some warm water ready for the baby.

859
01:08:29,560 --> 01:08:30,690
Right.

860
01:08:42,240 --> 01:08:43,530
Where the hell is it?

861
01:09:00,430 --> 01:09:02,550
I'm telling you...

862
01:09:02,640 --> 01:09:03,800
Shut him up.

863
01:09:04,100 --> 01:09:06,220
Be quiet. You're going to scare the baby.

864
01:09:06,930 --> 01:09:08,640
Are you telling me to shut up?

865
01:09:29,330 --> 01:09:31,370
Help me. Help!

866
01:09:31,460 --> 01:09:32,880
Somebody help--

867
01:09:39,090 --> 01:09:40,800
<i>I'm a cop without a sense of duty.</i>

868
01:09:42,180 --> 01:09:43,180
<i>I only became one</i>

869
01:09:43,800 --> 01:09:45,680
<i>to make a living.</i>

870
01:09:46,970 --> 01:09:48,810
<i>I've never been ashamed to say it.</i>

871
01:09:50,350 --> 01:09:51,480
<i>So,</i>

872
01:09:52,440 --> 01:09:53,730
<i>why am I running</i>

873
01:09:54,400 --> 01:09:56,190
<i>running as if my life depended on it?</i>

874
01:09:57,730 --> 01:09:59,150
One, two, three, four...

875
01:09:59,230 --> 01:10:01,110
<i>It's a job no one gives us credit for.</i>

876
01:10:01,200 --> 01:10:02,650
Again. One, two, three, four...

877
01:10:02,740 --> 01:10:05,370
<i>Tomorrow,
another case will be at the forefront.</i>

878
01:10:05,450 --> 01:10:06,740
One, two, three, four...

879
01:10:06,830 --> 01:10:08,870
<i>Those who appreciate us</i>

880
01:10:10,450 --> 01:10:12,540
-<i>isn't the police force.
-We'll go around in turns.</i>

881
01:10:13,040 --> 01:10:14,580
<i>It's just our pitiful selves.</i>

882
01:10:17,380 --> 01:10:19,210
-One, two...
-Not so hard.

883
01:10:19,590 --> 01:10:20,420
A baby is fragile.

884
01:10:21,220 --> 01:10:22,800
Be careful.

885
01:10:25,760 --> 01:10:26,720
<i>Still,</i>

886
01:10:27,930 --> 01:10:29,930
<i>I wished for the baby to live.</i>

887
01:10:30,390 --> 01:10:31,810
Five, six, seven...

888
01:10:31,890 --> 01:10:34,350
<i>If there was another job for me,</i>

889
01:10:35,440 --> 01:10:37,230
<i>I'd gladly quit this one.</i>

890
01:10:37,310 --> 01:10:38,980
Five, six, seven, eight, nine, ten.

891
01:10:49,280 --> 01:10:50,240
One, two, three, four...

892
01:10:50,330 --> 01:10:51,910
<i>I have a weak sense of duty.</i>

893
01:10:53,620 --> 01:10:54,620
<i>But we...</i>

894
01:10:55,710 --> 01:10:57,500
<i>No, as long as I've met the baby now,</i>

895
01:11:01,420 --> 01:11:02,510
<i>I just hope</i>

896
01:11:03,970 --> 01:11:05,510
<i>that it'll live.</i>

897
01:11:41,460 --> 01:11:43,260
Attention. Salute!

898
01:11:45,470 --> 01:11:46,840
Isn't the baby adorable?

899
01:11:46,930 --> 01:11:47,800
It is.

900
01:11:47,890 --> 01:11:50,850
Wasn't that one grand retirement present?

901
